### ===== HEALTH CHECK =====
GET http://localhost:5000/api/health

### ===== AUTHENTICATION =====

### Register as Admin
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@ecommerce.com",
  "password": "Admin123",
  "first_name": "Admin",
  "last_name": "User",
  "role": "admin",
  "phone_number": "0712345678"
}

### Register as Sales Rep
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "salesrep@ecommerce.com",
  "password": "Rep123",
  "first_name": "John",
  "last_name": "Salesman",
  "role": "sales_rep",
  "phone_number": "0787654321"
}

### Login Admin
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@ecommerce.com",
  "password": "Admin123"
}

### Login Sales Rep
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "salesrep@ecommerce.com",
  "password": "Rep123"
}

