### ===== ORDERS (NORMAL CUSTOMER ORDER) =====

### Create Normal Order (No Auth Required)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "order_type": "normal",
  "customer_name": "James Kipchoge",
  "customer_phone": "+254712345678",
  "customer_location_id": 1,
  "items": [
    {
      "product_id": 1,
      "quantity": 2
    },
    {
      "product_id": 2,
      "quantity": 5
    }
  ],
  "notes": "Please deliver ASAP"
}

